Parliament, Monday, 23 January 2023 – The Standing Committee on Public Accounts (SCOPA) will tomorrow meet with the Eskom Board and executives on its recommendations and reports as adopted by the National Assembly.
	
	SCOPA’s recommendations stem from its oversight visits to Eskom in 2019 and 2022.
	
	Details of the meeting are as follows: 
	Date: Tuesday, 24 January 2023
	Time: 09:30
	Venue: Committee Room M314, Third Floor, Marks Building.
	
	Please note that this will only be a physical meeting and no virtual meeting link will be available. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES.
	
	For media enquiries, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
	Name: Ms Faith Ndenze
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8268
	Cell: 081 377 0686
